{"tid":262594,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日放假，今晚食豪d","createTime":"2017-05-29T10:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T10:59:24.000Z","uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dca31b28b82333f2ac5b824b8c3a407fdb221a5d","tid":262594,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:49:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://holland.pk/fkhlp98e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffkhlp98e&d=QW2rtRgOdMk2gu85WiT3b8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=4833c029\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/fkhlp98e</a><br />\n今餐係我上次個po既晚餐白粥，炒麵，油炸鬼$21一倍價錢$42<br />\n<br />\n米線加底，通菜，大腸，雞翼，蘿蔔<br />\n<br />\n蘿蔔夠甜又夠晒口感好爽，<br />\n鹵水雞翼少少甜又唔老好滑，<br />\n大腸中上，有咬感但太短，唔夠入味<br />\n通菜普普通通<br />\n米線加埋底份量都係唔夠多，<br />\n最後我加埋辣辣油簡直畫龍點睛，個車仔麵即刻生猛晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過$42冇野飲真係貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35c3ffd854f50e84793accd8bdcf8c25071b009","tid":262594,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fkhlp98e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffkhlp98e&h=57cb457a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28a2542dac29c1c537d3047b374a5f4a0b8d34f1","tid":262594,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:53:00.000Z","msg":"正呀，我車仔麵都食開四餸的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b55af70afdf1333c0026bc4a75e41a2392648d","tid":262594,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正呀，我車仔麵都食開四餸的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你食幾錢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a863d43788c4c6b978743eca62bc582a113d32","tid":262594,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime